# Animations

- Prefer `transform` and `opacity` — avoid animating width/height
- Stagger children with `transition={{ delay: index * 0.1 }}`
- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion: reduce` — disable motion
- Lazy-load heavy 3D; use CSS gradient blobs as fallback
- Lenis wraps app in `SmoothScrollProvider`
